				\begin{document}$$if\ \#\left(peaks\in R\right)&gt;800$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M10" display="block"><mml:mrow><mml:mi>i</mml:mi><mml:mi>f</mml:mi><mml:mspace width="4pt"/><mml:mo>#</mml:mo><mml:mfenced close=")" open="("><mml:mi>p</mml:mi><mml:mi>e</mml:mi><mml:mi>a</mml:mi><mml:mi>k</mml:mi><mml:mi>s</mml:mi><mml:mo>∈</mml:mo><mml:mi>R</mml:mi></mml:mfenced><mml:mo>&gt;</mml:mo><mml:mn>800</mml:mn></mml:mrow></mml:math><graphic xlink:href="13059_2023_3096_Article_Eque.gif" position="anchor"/></alternatives></disp-formula>where the denominator is set to 800 (that is, the average number of mass peaks per genome in the database) for reference genomes/peak lists with more than 800 masses.</p></list-item><list-item><p id="Par36">Scoring scheme III:<disp-formula id="Equf"><alternatives><tex-math id="M11">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
